if {show_crepus}
  div class="popup popup--help"
    div class="popup__nav"
      button class="popup__back" type="button" data-action="hide-crepus"
        "← Help"
    h1 class="popup__title"
      "Crepus syntax"
    div class="popup__help-section"
      p class="popup__copy"
        "Crepus is an indent-based template language. Children are indented one level below their parent."
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Elements"
      pre class="popup__prompt"
        "tag class1 class2 attr=\"val\" dynattr={expr}
  \"child text with {variable} interpolation\"
  span another-class
    \"{nested}\""
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Conditionals"
      pre class="popup__prompt"
        "if {condition}
  div
    \"shown when true\"
else if {other}
  span
    \"else-if branch\"
else
  span
    \"fallback\""
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Loops"
      pre class="popup__prompt"
        "for item in {items}
  div row
    \"{item.name} — {item.value}\""
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Match"
      pre class="popup__prompt"
        "match {status}
  \"ok\" =>
    span green
      \"Success\"
  \"error\" =>
    span red
      \"Failed\"
  _ =>
    span
      \"Unknown\""
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Variables"
      pre class="popup__prompt"
        "$: let label = {\"Hello, \" + name}
$: default title = {\"Untitled\"}"
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Include"
      pre class="popup__prompt"
        "include ui.crepus#Button label=\"Click\" count={total}"
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Component file (ui.crepus)"
      pre class="popup__prompt"
        "+++
[Button.defaults]
label = \"Click\"
variant = \"primary\"
+++

--- Button
button {variant}
  \"{label}\""
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Data attributes for actions"
      pre class="popup__prompt"
        "button primary type=\"button\" data-action=\"submit\" data-id={item.id}
  \"Submit\""
      p class="popup__copy"
        "Any data-* attribute is collected and passed to handle_popup_action as the data map."
else if {show_help}
  div class="popup popup--help"
    div class="popup__nav"
      button class="popup__back" type="button" data-action="hide-help"
        "← Back"
    h1 class="popup__title"
      "How to use AI Anywhere"
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "What it does"
      p class="popup__copy"
        "AI Anywhere scans AI assistant pages for special widget tags in responses and renders them as interactive panels — charts, forms, visualisations, and more."
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Add this to your AI system prompt"
      p class="popup__copy"
        "Paste the following into your AI's system prompt or custom instructions:"
      div class="popup__code-block"
        div class="popup__code-header"
          span class="popup__code-label"
            "System prompt"
          button class="popup__copy-btn" type="button" data-action="copy-prompt"
            span class="material-symbols-outlined"
              "content_copy"
            "Copy"
        pre class="popup__prompt" id="system-prompt"
          "{system_prompt}"
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Rendering"
      p class="popup__copy"
        "Widgets appear below AI messages. Click Render to run them in a sandboxed iframe. Enable Auto-render to run them automatically."
    div class="popup__help-section"
      h2 class="popup__help-heading"
        "Legacy format"
      p class="popup__copy"
        "Code blocks with widget-html / widget-css / widget-js fences also work."
    div class="popup__help-section"
      button class="popup__crepus-btn" type="button" data-action="show-crepus"
        "Crepus syntax reference →"
else
  div class="popup"
    div class="popup__eyebrow"
      "crepuscularity"
    div class="popup__header"
      h1 class="popup__title"
        "AI Anywhere"
      button class="popup__help-btn" type="button" data-action="show-help" title="How to use"
        "?"
    p class="popup__copy"
      "Scan AI assistant pages for code blocks and render them as interactive widgets."
    label class="popup__toggle"
      if {enabled}
        input type="checkbox" id="enabled" data-action="set-enabled" checked
      else
        input type="checkbox" id="enabled" data-action="set-enabled"
      span
        "Enable scanner"
    label class="popup__toggle"
      if {auto_render}
        input type="checkbox" id="autoRender" data-action="set-auto-render" checked
      else
        input type="checkbox" id="autoRender" data-action="set-auto-render"
      span
        "Auto-render widgets"
